  => "interpretation: a13 explains ~29% of a14_R2 linear variance"
  => "by OLS normal equations: sum(a14_perp) = 0 AND sum(a14_perp * a13) = 0"
  => "→ Pearson(a14_perp, a13) = 0 exactly (by construction)"
  => "Spearman(a14_perp, a13) = +0.022 (rank-correlation also near-zero — not a linear-only artifact)"

